# GLOBAL SEARCH PAGE

Endpoint:

/api/search/globalSearch

This is the flagship feature of AYD and should be treated as the primary product experience.

The design quality of this page should exceed the rest of the application.

## Search Interface

At the top:

* Large search input
* Search button
* Enter key triggers search

Below the search box:

### Text Filter

One general text filter section:

* text input
* operator dropdown

Only send to backend when populated.

### Numeric and Date Filters

IMPORTANT:

The frontend must inspect the schema of ALL tables inside the currently selected workspace.

Only columns with datatype:

* number
* integer
* float
* decimal
* date
* datetime
* timestamp

should generate advanced filters.

Do NOT generate filters for string/text columns beyond the main text filter.

For every numeric/date column discovered:

Display:

* Table Name
* Column Name
* Operator Dropdown
* Value Input

Examples:

Orders.createdAt
[After ▼]
[2025-01-01]

Products.price
[Greater Than ▼]
[100]

Customer.age
[Between ▼]
[18 - 65]

All filter fields are optional.

Only populated filters should be included in the request payload.

## Search Results

IMPORTANT:

Do NOT group results by table.

The backend returns relevance-ranked hybrid search results.

The frontend must preserve backend ranking order exactly as received.

Results should be displayed as a ranked list.

Each result card should contain:

* Relevance Score
* Matching Fields
* Highlighted Matching Values

The relevance score should be visually emphasized.

Example:

Score: 97.8

Matched Fields:

* name
* description

Record Data:
{ ... }

Results must remain sorted by score descending.

Never reorder results on the frontend.

## UX Requirements

Loading State

* skeleton loaders
* animated search progress

No Results State

* professional empty state
* suggestions for refining search

Error State

* retry button

## Performance

Debounce filter updates.

Only trigger search when:

* Search button clicked
* Enter key pressed

Do not automatically search while typing.


